metadata.name: lost in space
metadata.description:
One of the entrees in the Rik Oostenbroek's "Self" collaborative project.

To be able to participate in such a contest is already a blessing itself. This showed me the many possibilities that I had in mind, wondering which would be the best take on this project.

This project had over 400 artists that reimagined what "Self" meant to them. A true solidarity in the community by uplifting others. Looking forward to more in the future.
